{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10106712907443-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10106712907443-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100076776275-2"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外短文，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":720,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>被人相信是一种幸福（节选）</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一艘货轮在烟波浩渺的大西洋上行驶。一个在船尾做勤杂的黑人小孩不慎掉进了波涛滚滚的大西洋。孩子大喊救命，无奈风大浪急，船上的人谁也没听见，他（ ）地看着货轮拖着浪花越走越远……<br></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">求生的本能使孩子在冰冷的水里拼命地游，他用全身的力气挥动着瘦小的双臂，努力把头伸出水面，（ ）盯着轮船远去的方向。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">船越走越远，船身越来越小，到后来，什么都看不见了，只剩下一望无际的汪洋。孩子的力气也快用完了，实在游不动了，他觉得自己要沉下去了。放弃吧，他对自己说。这时候，他想起了老船长那张慈祥的脸和友善的眼神，_____！想到这里，孩子鼓起勇气用生命的最后力量又朝前游去……    </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">船长终于发现那黑人小孩失踪了，当他断定孩子是掉进海里后，下令返航，回去找。这时有人规劝：“这么长时间了，就是没有被淹没，也让鲨鱼吃了……”船长犹豫了一下，还是决定回去找。又有人说：“为了一个黑奴孩子，值得吗？”船长（ ）：“住嘴！”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">终于，在那孩子就要沉下去的最后一刻，船长赶到了，救起了孩子。   </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当孩子苏醒过来之后，跪在地上感谢船长的救命之恩时，船长扶起孩子问：“孩子，你怎么能坚持这么长时间？”   </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">孩子回答：“我知道您会来救我的。一定会的。”    </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“你怎么知道我一定会来救你的？” </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“因为我知道您是那样的人！”  </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">听到这里，白发苍苍的船长“扑通”一声跪在黑人孩子面前，（ ）：“孩子，不是我救了你，而是你救了我啊！我为我在那一刻的动摇而耻辱……”   </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一个人能被他人相信也是一种幸福，他人在绝望时想起你，相信你会给予拯救更是一种幸福。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">选择词语填入下面空白处。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">（1）他__$$__地看着货轮拖着浪花越走越远……</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">（2）__$$__盯着轮船远去的方向。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">（3）船长__$$__：“住嘴！”</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">（4）白发苍苍的船长“扑通”一声跪在黑人孩子面前，__$$__：“孩子，不是我救了你，而是你救了我啊！”</p>","answers":[{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100075999195","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":10,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"大喝一声","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"睁大眼睛","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"泪流满面","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"眼睁睁","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101006],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"<p>写出下面词语在原文